OL,3,CSummary of evidence in Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson trial underway
OL,6,FA judge has begun summarising the
OL,7,Fevidence in the sexual offences trial
OL,8,Fof former DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,9,FDonaldson.
OL,11,FThe jury will retire to consider its
OL,12,Fverdict after Judge Paul Ramsey
OL,13,Ffinishes delivering his charge.
OL,15,FThe 63-year-old former MP has pleaded
OL,16,Fnot guilty to 18 alleged offences.
