OL,3,CSummary of evidence in Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson trial underway
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a period
OL,9,Fbetween 1985 and 2008 involving two
OL,10,Falleged victims.
OL,12,FDonaldson, wearing a dark grey suit
OL,13,Fand a pink tie, sat in the dock at the
OL,14,Fback of the court with his arms folded
OL,15,Fwhile the judge delivered his remarks.
OL,17,FThe judge told the jury: "We are now
OL,18,Freaching the closing stages of the
OL,19,Ftrial."
