OL,3,CSummary of evidence in Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson trial underway
OL,6,FHe said the jurors had to be satisfied
OL,7,Fthat the prosecution had proven the
OL,8,Fcase against Donaldson beyond
OL,9,Freasonable doubt before they could
OL,10,Fconvict.
OL,12,FComplainants A and B have both given
OL,13,Fevidence at the trial.
OL,15,FBoth women allege they were abused as
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FDonaldson spent two days giving
OL,19,Fevidence during the trial.
